WEBVTT

01:30.770 --> 01:35.039
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.390 --> 01:38.880
[2025] [Shengcheng Jinxing Co., Ltd]

01:43.120 --> 01:43.710
Ms. Xia.

01:44.200 --> 01:45.039
Sorry to keep you waiting.

01:45.039 --> 01:46.420
It's okay. I just got here.

01:46.420 --> 01:46.840
Please sit.

01:46.840 --> 01:47.200
Okay.

01:48.479 --> 01:48.940
Give me.

01:50.680 --> 01:51.150
As for the contract,

01:51.150 --> 01:52.640
we've finalized it on our side.

01:52.640 --> 01:53.200
Now all that's left

01:53.200 --> 01:54.590
is for you to sign and stamp it.

01:54.590 --> 01:55.190
All right.

01:56.759 --> 01:57.430
It's printed exactly according to

01:57.430 --> 01:58.039
the version we previously

01:58.039 --> 01:59.120
agreed upon.

01:59.310 --> 02:00.770
There won't be any issues.

02:06.840 --> 02:07.950
It's the end of the month today,

02:07.950 --> 02:09.680
and also the end of the quarter.

02:10.000 --> 02:11.030
If we wrap things up quickly,

02:11.030 --> 02:12.560
this payment can still count towards

02:12.560 --> 02:13.590
your performance for this month.

02:13.590 --> 02:14.190
Am I right?

02:15.910 --> 02:17.520
The business terms are fine.

02:18.079 --> 02:20.079
The 8 major clauses of the contract,

02:20.280 --> 02:22.140
totaling 13 pages, are also fine.

02:22.470 --> 02:23.150
No issues here.

02:23.150 --> 02:23.800
Then,

02:24.150 --> 02:25.210
thank you, Mr. Jia.

02:27.190 --> 02:28.590
If one lives to 70,

02:29.280 --> 02:30.400
their lifetime consists of about

02:30.400 --> 02:31.600
2.2 billion seconds.

02:32.310 --> 02:33.800
We can never predict

02:34.470 --> 02:35.310
which exact second

02:35.310 --> 02:36.120
will be

02:36.870 --> 02:38.120
life-changing.

02:38.400 --> 02:40.120
Here's to a successful cooperation.

02:40.120 --> 02:40.650
Alright.

02:40.960 --> 02:41.800
I won't see you out then.

02:41.800 --> 02:42.460
No problem.

02:50.120 --> 02:50.680
Ms. Xia.

02:50.840 --> 02:51.640
What's wrong?

02:51.840 --> 02:52.370
Nothing.

02:52.400 --> 02:54.030
My eyelid keeps twitching lately.

02:54.030 --> 02:55.360
It makes me feel uneasy.

02:56.360 --> 02:56.890
Let's go.

03:01.230 --> 03:04.810
[Episode 32]
[The Life-Changing Moment]

03:27.120 --> 03:27.650
Xiaolan.

03:36.780 --> 03:37.430
It's time.

03:44.630 --> 03:45.160
Let's go.

03:46.310 --> 03:47.770
Your dream is right ahead.

03:50.700 --> 03:52.160
It's waiting for me ahead.

04:06.120 --> 04:07.430
It's quite large-scale, isn't it?

04:07.430 --> 04:08.750
Yeah. Thanks to you,

04:08.840 --> 04:09.430
Mr. Mao.

04:11.000 --> 04:12.710
Xiaolan deserves most of the credit.

04:12.710 --> 04:14.240
The credit is mainly yours.

04:14.870 --> 04:15.870
Hurry up, you two.

04:15.870 --> 04:16.800
Put them here.

04:18.050 --> 04:18.870
Place them properly.

04:18.870 --> 04:20.040
Make sure everything over there
is checked.

04:20.040 --> 04:21.600
Quick, get these displayed.

04:21.600 --> 04:22.930
Or we'll run out of time.

04:23.310 --> 04:24.510
Hello, Chairman Du.

04:24.600 --> 04:25.680
Is Xia Xiaolan not here yet?

04:25.680 --> 04:26.360
Not yet.

04:26.800 --> 04:27.510
Manager Ge.

04:28.160 --> 04:29.620
When will Xiaolan be here?

04:29.630 --> 04:30.870
And by the way, about last night—

04:30.870 --> 04:31.730
what happened?

04:32.110 --> 04:32.570
Yest...

04:32.680 --> 04:33.040
Let's wait a bit longe...

04:33.040 --> 04:33.700
She's here.

04:35.430 --> 04:35.750
Mom.

04:35.750 --> 04:36.240
Xiaolan.

04:36.240 --> 04:37.240
-We've been waiting for you.
-Mr. Mao.

04:37.240 --> 04:37.700
Auntie.

04:39.070 --> 04:40.070
It's about time.

04:40.310 --> 04:40.920
Ge Jian.

04:41.159 --> 04:42.070
Let's get started.

04:42.070 --> 04:42.930
Got it, Ms. Xia.

04:47.380 --> 04:50.060
[Golden Sands Pool—Qi Hang Property]

05:06.000 --> 05:07.240
Welcome to

05:07.360 --> 05:08.600
Golden Sands Pool.

05:46.870 --> 05:47.680
Congratulations, Mr. Xia,

05:47.680 --> 05:49.630
on becoming a homeowner
in Golden Sands Pool.

05:49.630 --> 05:50.600
Crack the golden egg,

05:50.600 --> 05:52.060
and good luck will follow.

06:04.950 --> 06:06.280
Please watch the steps.

06:06.480 --> 06:07.010
This way.

06:07.630 --> 06:09.270
This is the reception room.

06:09.600 --> 06:11.830
And this is the Western-style dining room.

06:11.830 --> 06:12.600
The prices we quote are for

06:12.600 --> 06:14.560
standard delivery units
with no interior decoration included.

06:14.560 --> 06:15.000
Okay.

06:16.000 --> 06:16.660
Hello, Sir.

06:16.760 --> 06:17.400
Pardon me,

06:17.430 --> 06:19.230
but smoking is prohibited here.

06:32.870 --> 06:33.930
Golden Sands Pool?

06:34.120 --> 06:34.630
The one with apartments going for

06:34.630 --> 06:36.230
2,000 yuan per square meter.

06:36.510 --> 06:38.970
They even throw in household registration.

06:39.000 --> 06:39.480
Dajun.

06:40.159 --> 06:41.690
Isn't that Young Master Du?

06:44.560 --> 06:45.190
Do you want to go...

06:45.190 --> 06:45.920
It's not him.

06:46.390 --> 06:47.720
You must've seen wrong.

06:56.870 --> 06:57.400
Add it in.

06:57.600 --> 06:57.930
Okay.

06:57.950 --> 06:58.480
Alright.

06:58.870 --> 06:59.400
Xiaolan.

06:59.600 --> 07:00.860
There's a call for you.

07:03.510 --> 07:03.950
Hello?

07:05.950 --> 07:07.150
Luo Yaozong is awake?

07:07.980 --> 07:09.630
It's not that we won't let you in.

07:09.630 --> 07:11.090
This involves a homicide.

07:11.190 --> 07:12.190
We have to wait for the police

07:12.190 --> 07:13.000
to arrive.

07:13.040 --> 07:13.680
Why wait for the police?

07:13.680 --> 07:14.720
My son is lying in there!

07:14.720 --> 07:16.230
Why can't I go in to see my son?

07:16.230 --> 07:16.830
What are you doing...

07:16.830 --> 07:17.430
She's right.

07:17.430 --> 07:17.800
Chief Luo.

07:17.800 --> 07:19.330
Since my grandson is awake,

07:19.390 --> 07:20.920
I have the right to see him.

07:21.750 --> 07:22.830
She's right.

07:23.070 --> 07:24.160
Now that Luo Yaozong is awake,

07:24.160 --> 07:24.920
we need to conduct

07:24.920 --> 07:26.250
a routine questioning.

07:29.480 --> 07:30.630
Hello. How is he doing?

07:30.630 --> 07:31.720
Can he be questioned?

07:31.720 --> 07:33.430
The patient's injuries are quite severe.

07:33.430 --> 07:34.800
Although he's currently awake,

07:34.800 --> 07:36.360
it's not advisable to engage him in
much conversation.

07:36.360 --> 07:37.090
Understood.

07:37.480 --> 07:39.390
We'll just ask him a few key questions.

07:39.390 --> 07:39.830
Okay.

07:42.600 --> 07:43.680
He's awake?

07:44.560 --> 07:45.020
That...

07:45.480 --> 07:46.120
That Xia Xiaolan

07:46.120 --> 07:47.390
is just too lucky.

07:48.510 --> 07:49.040
Yixiong,

07:49.240 --> 07:49.920
calm down.

07:52.360 --> 07:52.920
Yixiong,

07:52.950 --> 07:53.720
don't worry.

07:53.870 --> 07:55.560
I had Mosquito from Kong Island

07:55.560 --> 07:56.680
handle this.

07:57.159 --> 07:57.920
I had made everything

07:57.920 --> 07:58.720
clear to them.

07:58.920 --> 08:00.830
There's no way
they can trace it back to us.

08:00.830 --> 08:01.680
You... I...

08:03.800 --> 08:05.000
For such a big deal,

08:05.270 --> 08:06.560
you had someone

08:06.560 --> 08:08.420
fresh from Kong Island handle it?

08:09.680 --> 08:10.430
It's not like that.

08:10.430 --> 08:11.000
Yixiong.

08:11.480 --> 08:12.120
You know,

08:12.390 --> 08:13.360
since Liu

08:13.360 --> 08:15.270
was reported by Bai Zhenzhu
and got taken in,

08:15.270 --> 08:16.310
the police have been watching

08:16.310 --> 08:17.430
our men too closely.

08:17.430 --> 08:18.430
We're really short-handed...

08:18.430 --> 08:19.430
Shut up!

08:19.870 --> 08:20.510
Get out!

08:23.630 --> 08:25.830
You can't even handle such a small task.

08:26.160 --> 08:27.680
I'll smack you!

08:48.790 --> 08:49.870
I need to go to Kong Island.

08:49.870 --> 08:51.000
As soon as possible.

08:51.510 --> 08:52.240
Luo Yaozong.

08:52.790 --> 08:53.670
Do you remember

08:53.670 --> 08:55.000
how you fell last night?

09:01.270 --> 09:01.800
Let's go.

09:03.270 --> 09:03.750
Move.

09:09.270 --> 09:09.720
Move.

09:13.350 --> 09:14.810
Falling from this height,

09:15.240 --> 09:16.700
he's definitely done for.

09:16.910 --> 09:18.240
Where am I?

09:18.910 --> 09:20.080
It's so cold.

09:21.120 --> 09:23.980
We're taking you somewhere else
for another round.

09:25.240 --> 09:25.750
Buddy.

09:26.750 --> 09:28.680
Don't blame me for not helping you.

09:28.960 --> 09:30.360
When you get to the other side,

09:30.360 --> 09:32.150
I'll burn you plenty of joss paper.

09:32.150 --> 09:32.980
I drank too much...

09:32.980 --> 09:33.440
Come on.

09:33.790 --> 09:34.850
What are you doing?

09:38.650 --> 09:39.510
So,

09:39.510 --> 09:40.840
the last people you saw were

09:40.840 --> 09:42.240
Zhang Bing and Zhang Tao?

09:44.900 --> 09:45.510
And then?

09:47.080 --> 09:47.940
You were drunk,

09:48.790 --> 09:50.390
so you didn't know anything.

09:50.850 --> 09:52.060
When you woke up,

09:52.320 --> 09:53.920
you were already on the roof.

09:54.030 --> 09:56.030
It was Zhang Bing who pushed you off,

09:56.360 --> 09:56.840
right?

10:00.550 --> 10:01.960
Given his condition,

10:02.150 --> 10:02.720
we won't be able to

10:02.720 --> 10:04.320
get more details out of him anytime soon.

10:04.320 --> 10:05.650
Let's call it a day then.

10:05.840 --> 10:06.440
Let's step outside.

10:06.440 --> 10:07.030
Yaozong.

10:07.750 --> 10:09.320
Focus on recovering.

10:09.570 --> 10:11.120
I won't let that bastard
who pushed you off

10:11.120 --> 10:12.120
get away with it.

10:15.510 --> 10:16.320
Officers.

10:17.000 --> 10:18.530
You must catch the culprit.

10:19.030 --> 10:20.290
He's the only heir left

10:20.510 --> 10:22.480
of our Luo family.

10:23.910 --> 10:25.440
My grandson's a victim.

10:26.510 --> 10:28.710
Zhang Bing and Zhang Tao are murderers.

10:28.750 --> 10:30.060
They must be executed!

10:30.150 --> 10:30.950
That's right.

10:31.360 --> 10:32.030
Sir,

10:32.600 --> 10:34.530
sentencing isn't up to the police.

10:34.670 --> 10:35.960
But this case

10:35.960 --> 10:37.690
has indeed been reclassified.

10:37.720 --> 10:39.000
I'll head back to the station right now

10:39.000 --> 10:39.960
to re-interrogate those two

10:39.960 --> 10:41.350
who pretended to steal steel,

10:41.350 --> 10:43.320
and arrest Zhang Bing and Zhang Tao
as soon as possible.

10:43.320 --> 10:44.550
Whatever you need from us,

10:44.550 --> 10:45.720
we're ready to assist in any way.

10:45.720 --> 10:46.120
Okay.

10:47.600 --> 10:48.270
Yaozong.

10:48.960 --> 10:49.910
If you remember anything,

10:49.910 --> 10:51.370
be sure to tell the police.

10:57.670 --> 10:58.200
Ms. Xia,

10:58.390 --> 10:59.910
I'll head back to the station first.

10:59.910 --> 11:01.320
Officer Zhou will take over from now

11:01.320 --> 11:02.150
and follow up on the rest.

11:02.150 --> 11:03.030
Okay, thank you.

11:03.030 --> 11:03.960
Okay, thank you.

11:05.870 --> 11:06.330
Well...

11:06.870 --> 11:07.480
Mr. Luo.

11:08.030 --> 11:08.910
It wasn't easy

11:08.910 --> 11:10.750
for your precious grandson to survive.

11:10.750 --> 11:12.750
Don't start
getting any crooked ideas again

11:12.750 --> 11:14.150
just because he's awake.

11:14.600 --> 11:15.530
You heard it too.

11:15.790 --> 11:16.480
The doctor said

11:16.480 --> 11:18.340
his condition is still critical.

11:19.340 --> 11:20.820
And all his medical bills

11:21.240 --> 11:23.480
are being paid by Ms. Xia.

11:25.000 --> 11:26.880
You guys should stay with him
for a couple more days.

11:26.880 --> 11:28.080
He needs company now.

11:28.600 --> 11:29.790
You heard it too—

11:30.240 --> 11:31.840
he was pushed off by someone,

11:32.150 --> 11:34.150
and that person still hasn’t been found.

11:34.150 --> 11:35.550
If they find out

11:35.670 --> 11:37.270
that Luo Yaozong isn't dead,

11:37.630 --> 11:38.430
I'm afraid...

11:38.670 --> 11:39.600
Then... Then...

11:39.670 --> 11:40.480
Dad. Dad.

11:40.870 --> 11:42.390
The most important thing right now

11:42.390 --> 11:43.720
is that Yaozong is okay.

11:43.840 --> 11:44.170
Then...

11:44.170 --> 11:45.230
Alright, alright.

11:45.390 --> 11:45.920
Let's go.

11:46.150 --> 11:46.680
Let's go.

12:09.390 --> 12:10.600
Forty-seven units—

12:10.720 --> 12:12.670
a total of 7,892,300 yuan!

12:13.050 --> 12:17.160
♪ I'm not willing to be ordinary ♪

12:16.120 --> 12:18.120
Forty-seven units sold on the first day.

12:18.120 --> 12:19.080
Only 4 buyers

12:18.250 --> 12:20.710
♪ Sometimes I also want to
go a little crazy ♪

12:19.080 --> 12:20.270
chose mortgage financing;

12:20.270 --> 12:21.360
the other 43 buyers

12:21.270 --> 12:24.230
♪ Once I've decided, I'll be brave ♪

12:21.360 --> 12:22.670
all chose to pay in full

12:22.750 --> 12:23.870
within 3 days.

12:24.200 --> 12:24.910
This way,

12:24.940 --> 12:27.530
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

12:25.080 --> 12:25.960
we'll be able to pay off

12:25.960 --> 12:27.760
the first batch of the bank loan.

12:28.630 --> 12:30.200
Now that we can pay off half of the loan
in one go,

12:28.720 --> 12:30.940
♪ There are laughter and tears ♪

12:30.390 --> 12:31.510
with over 90 units left,

12:31.510 --> 12:32.910
we'll make over 8 million!

12:32.020 --> 12:34.820
♪ There's joy and sorrow ♪

12:33.600 --> 12:34.320
Xiaolan.

12:35.110 --> 12:38.150
♪ But this is life ♪

12:35.120 --> 12:37.120
You've worked hard for so many years—

12:37.120 --> 12:38.270
isn't this the day
you've been waiting for?

12:38.270 --> 12:38.790
Yeah.

12:39.200 --> 12:40.550
Congrats. Congrats.

12:40.130 --> 12:43.760
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

12:40.550 --> 12:41.680
You finally made it!

12:42.150 --> 12:42.960
Congrats, Xiaolan!

12:42.960 --> 12:43.780
Congrats, Xiaolan.

12:43.780 --> 12:47.080
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

12:44.200 --> 12:45.600
Congratulations!

12:47.110 --> 12:50.010
♪ We never give up ♪

12:50.830 --> 12:53.960
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

12:53.980 --> 12:57.200
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

12:55.030 --> 12:57.720
Victory, invincible, long live—

12:57.230 --> 13:00.450
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

12:58.750 --> 12:59.750
none of these words

12:59.750 --> 13:00.630
are enough to describe

13:00.630 --> 13:01.790
how I feel right now.

13:00.820 --> 13:03.760
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

13:03.120 --> 13:03.870
A dream

13:03.870 --> 13:05.000
I've had over and over,

13:04.140 --> 13:07.000
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

13:05.750 --> 13:07.510
a breath I've held back for so long,

13:07.510 --> 13:13.900
♪ That'd be enough ♪

13:08.150 --> 13:09.750
and desires once buried

13:09.870 --> 13:11.790
beneath the trivialities of my past life—

13:11.790 --> 13:13.590
all of it was waiting to burst out

13:13.960 --> 13:15.090
in this very moment.

13:20.320 --> 13:21.920
Great work today, everyone!

13:22.200 --> 13:22.670
Ge Jian,

13:23.030 --> 13:24.170
get everyone together.

13:24.170 --> 13:27.390
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

13:24.390 --> 13:25.870
San's Food Stall tonight—

13:25.870 --> 13:26.870
dinner's on me!

13:27.120 --> 13:27.910
Great!

13:27.420 --> 13:30.640
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

13:27.910 --> 13:29.440
Thanks, Xiaolan!

13:30.630 --> 13:31.390
Let's go!

13:31.010 --> 13:33.950
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

13:31.480 --> 13:32.010
Let's go!

13:34.330 --> 13:37.190
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

13:34.550 --> 13:35.390
So happy.

13:35.670 --> 13:36.270
Xiaolan.

13:36.550 --> 13:37.840
You young people go celebrate.

13:37.700 --> 13:44.090
♪ That'd be enough ♪

13:37.840 --> 13:38.770
I won't join you.

13:38.960 --> 13:40.160
I'm meeting a friend.

13:40.550 --> 13:41.200
Mr. Mao.

13:41.670 --> 13:42.330
Please sit.

13:45.240 --> 13:45.910
Mr. Mao.

13:46.910 --> 13:47.720
Thank you.

13:48.870 --> 13:50.630
Golden Sands Pool is the first project

13:50.630 --> 13:52.550
I designed independently after graduation.

13:52.550 --> 13:53.610
Without your help,

13:53.910 --> 13:55.440
I wouldn't be who I am today.

13:56.030 --> 13:56.870
Enough with

13:56.870 --> 13:57.960
the pleasantries.

13:58.410 --> 13:59.720
After the celebration,

13:59.720 --> 14:01.480
get back to the office right away.

14:01.480 --> 14:04.320
There are a whole bunch of issues
from the project process

14:04.320 --> 14:05.920
I need to go through with you.

14:06.200 --> 14:07.120
Yes, sure.

14:07.270 --> 14:08.750
I still have much to learn,

14:08.750 --> 14:10.150
and I need your guidance.

14:11.440 --> 14:12.000
Mr. Mao.

14:18.910 --> 14:19.440
Here.

14:20.960 --> 14:21.420
This...

14:24.150 --> 14:24.630
What,

14:25.870 --> 14:27.270
are you giving me a house?

14:28.960 --> 14:29.910
I've been paid

14:29.910 --> 14:31.320
my full salary and bonuses.

14:31.320 --> 14:32.150
I can't accept this.

14:32.150 --> 14:33.350
Don't pull this on me.

14:33.480 --> 14:34.680
I'm not accepting it.

14:35.200 --> 14:36.270
Mr. Mao.

14:36.550 --> 14:38.350
I know you're a stubborn old man.

14:38.670 --> 14:39.840
But don't forget—

14:39.960 --> 14:41.290
I'm a stubborn girl too.

14:41.600 --> 14:42.750
Whatever I want to do,

14:42.750 --> 14:43.750
I will get it done.

14:44.220 --> 14:44.670
Just take this

14:44.670 --> 14:45.390
as a token of respect

14:45.390 --> 14:47.000
from a student to her teacher.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.000
Please accept it.

14:53.600 --> 14:55.910
Alright then, thank you.

14:56.440 --> 14:57.040
Thank you.

14:59.000 --> 14:59.750
Mr. Mao.

15:00.440 --> 15:01.240
This time,

15:01.600 --> 15:03.080
don't give your nice apartment away

15:03.080 --> 15:04.410
to your children again.

15:04.870 --> 15:06.510
You've worked hard your whole life.

15:06.510 --> 15:08.510
It's time for you to enjoy yourself.

15:08.750 --> 15:10.360
If your children want a nice apartment,

15:10.360 --> 15:12.160
let them work for it themselves.

15:12.720 --> 15:13.750
Okay. Okay.

15:15.000 --> 15:16.400
Girl, I'll listen to you.

15:21.910 --> 15:22.870
Let's have a drink together!

15:22.870 --> 15:23.330
Come on!

15:24.200 --> 15:25.240
-To Ms. Xia!
-Ms. Xia!

15:25.240 --> 15:25.770
Alright.

15:25.960 --> 15:27.820
I'll save the pleasantries then.

15:27.870 --> 15:29.120
Bottoms up!

15:34.200 --> 15:35.390
Everyone, eat and drink

15:35.390 --> 15:36.960
to your heart's content tonight.

15:36.960 --> 15:39.080
We've still got a tough battle
to fight tomorrow.

15:39.080 --> 15:40.850
Once we finish selling all the apartments,

15:40.850 --> 15:42.790
I'll take you all on
a team-building outing.

15:42.790 --> 15:43.550
Team building?

15:43.550 --> 15:44.080
Team building?

15:44.080 --> 15:44.600
Ms. Xia,

15:44.910 --> 15:46.170
what is team building?

15:46.200 --> 15:47.080
Team building

15:47.080 --> 15:48.750
means taking all of you

15:48.750 --> 15:49.600
out for fun together!

15:49.600 --> 15:51.030
How about a trip to
Singapore, Malaysia, and Thailand?

15:51.030 --> 15:51.910
Great!

15:51.910 --> 15:53.120
Singapore, Malaysia, and Thailand!

15:53.120 --> 15:53.750
Ms. Xia.

15:53.870 --> 15:55.630
That tour route is super popular
right now.

15:55.630 --> 15:56.870
I really want to go!

15:56.870 --> 15:57.930
We'll definitely work hard.

15:57.930 --> 15:58.360
When the time comes,

15:58.360 --> 15:59.440
you just go and have fun
with peace of mind.

15:59.440 --> 16:01.300
I'll take care of your mom for you.

16:01.320 --> 16:03.030
You'd better focus on
doing your job well first.

16:03.030 --> 16:04.960
The upcoming sales are just as important.

16:04.960 --> 16:06.890
Li, you've got the right attitude.

16:08.080 --> 16:09.280
Our food's coming up.

16:09.360 --> 16:10.030
Come on.

16:11.200 --> 16:12.330
A substantial dish.

16:12.360 --> 16:13.600
Come on. Come on.

16:13.600 --> 16:14.030
Here.

16:17.790 --> 16:18.320
Alright.

16:19.840 --> 16:20.630
This dish

16:20.720 --> 16:21.750
is on me.

16:22.120 --> 16:23.780
Wishing you soaring ambition

16:23.840 --> 16:25.000
and victory from the start!

16:25.000 --> 16:26.550
-Well said!
-Well said!

16:26.630 --> 16:27.870
-Thank you, San.
-Thank you.

16:27.870 --> 16:28.670
San,

16:28.670 --> 16:29.600
every time we come here,

16:29.600 --> 16:30.750
you give us discounts and free dishes.

16:30.750 --> 16:32.320
We almost feel embarrassed to come again.

16:32.320 --> 16:34.080
We are also generating revenue for San
by coming here, right?

16:34.080 --> 16:34.600
Everyone is welcome!

16:34.600 --> 16:35.480
Come often!

16:35.480 --> 16:36.440
Yes, right.

16:38.630 --> 16:39.160
Xiaolan.

16:39.790 --> 16:41.050
Look, your apartments

16:42.630 --> 16:43.890
sell for 7 to 8 million,

16:44.240 --> 16:45.630
while all these tables added together

16:45.630 --> 16:46.910
won't make more than 700 yuan.

16:46.910 --> 16:47.550
When you have time

16:47.550 --> 16:48.200
from your busy schedule,

16:48.200 --> 16:49.530
give me some advice too.

16:49.670 --> 16:51.200
I'm not asking for huge wealth or fame.

16:51.200 --> 16:52.440
I just want to take the top spot

16:52.440 --> 16:53.570
on this food street.

16:54.750 --> 16:57.210
Otherwise, I'd feel
I don't deserve Ms. Bai.

16:57.720 --> 16:59.630
I heard that.

17:01.020 --> 17:02.220
Don't talk nonsense.

17:02.330 --> 17:02.960
I think the way you are now

17:02.960 --> 17:03.910
is good enough.

17:05.510 --> 17:06.200
San.

17:07.079 --> 17:08.849
Did someone just

17:08.880 --> 17:10.000
call you,

17:10.069 --> 17:11.530
asking for food delivery?

17:11.720 --> 17:12.550
To be honest,

17:12.920 --> 17:14.920
a while back, a regular customer of mine

17:14.920 --> 17:16.050
sprained his ankle.

17:16.230 --> 17:17.109
He couldn't come here,

17:17.109 --> 17:18.000
but he was craving our food.

17:18.000 --> 17:19.000
He really wanted to eat it,

17:19.000 --> 17:20.589
so I delivered it to him a few times.

17:20.589 --> 17:22.640
Now he wants me to deliver every day,

17:22.920 --> 17:25.270
and others found out
and want delivery too.

17:25.270 --> 17:25.790
Sure,

17:25.920 --> 17:27.510
delivery is convenient for them.

17:27.510 --> 17:28.200
But for me,

17:28.200 --> 17:29.860
I'm just too busy to handle it.

17:29.960 --> 17:30.720
Now I'm thinking,

17:30.720 --> 17:32.450
I shouldn't have started this.

17:32.830 --> 17:33.750
I think

17:33.750 --> 17:35.160
it's a great start.

17:35.440 --> 17:36.220
Think about it—

17:36.220 --> 17:38.310
where there's demand, there's a market.

17:38.310 --> 17:38.880
San,

17:39.200 --> 17:41.590
you could start a takeout service—

17:43.830 --> 17:45.760
that is, a food delivery business.

17:46.030 --> 17:46.960
Here's what you do:

17:46.960 --> 17:49.020
set up a dedicated line for ordering,

17:49.030 --> 17:50.440
and then hire a few people

17:50.550 --> 17:52.200
just to deliver the food.

17:53.880 --> 17:56.110
Then I'd have to hire more people.

17:57.200 --> 17:58.400
Hiring is not a problem.

17:58.400 --> 17:59.880
Zhenzhu's got several senior brothers

17:59.880 --> 18:01.070
still doing part-time jobs out there.

18:01.070 --> 18:01.920
That's right.

18:01.920 --> 18:02.920
I'm short

18:02.920 --> 18:03.720
on everything else,

18:03.720 --> 18:04.720
but not manpower.

18:05.030 --> 18:05.370
Right.

18:05.370 --> 18:06.680
Besides hiring people,

18:06.680 --> 18:08.720
you also need to buy a few motorcycles.

18:08.720 --> 18:10.240
You can set a delivery range,

18:10.240 --> 18:10.970
for example,

18:11.030 --> 18:12.530
3 or 5 kilometers,

18:12.680 --> 18:14.480
and promise a specific delivery time.

18:14.480 --> 18:15.000
This way,

18:15.000 --> 18:16.350
the food delivered is both warm

18:16.350 --> 18:17.160
and fresh.

18:17.160 --> 18:18.830
If customers feel safe and enjoy the food,

18:18.830 --> 18:20.360
they'll promote it for you.

18:21.440 --> 18:22.200
Will this work?

18:22.200 --> 18:23.160
With all the people and motorcycles,

18:23.160 --> 18:24.700
how much will the cost increase?

18:24.700 --> 18:25.640
Why wouldn't it work?

18:25.640 --> 18:27.440
It also increases your customer base.

18:27.440 --> 18:28.750
You can also charge

18:28.920 --> 18:30.160
a delivery fee as appropriate.

18:30.160 --> 18:31.000
Some people

18:31.000 --> 18:32.400
just don't want to go out.

18:32.400 --> 18:34.240
They'd rather spend a few extra yuan

18:34.240 --> 18:35.110
just to get your

18:35.200 --> 18:36.640
door-to-door service.

18:39.310 --> 18:40.040
Will it work?

18:40.770 --> 18:41.640
All these years,

18:41.640 --> 18:43.070
the ideas Xiaolan came up with

18:43.070 --> 18:44.160
have never failed.

18:44.240 --> 18:44.640
Here.

18:44.830 --> 18:46.270
Hurry up and toast Ms. Xia.

18:46.270 --> 18:46.800
Alright.

18:46.830 --> 18:48.000
I'll start tomorrow.

18:48.000 --> 18:48.270
Okay.

18:48.270 --> 18:48.640
Come on.

18:48.640 --> 18:49.480
Let's toast Ms. Xia together.

18:49.480 --> 18:50.830
Let's all toast Ms. Xia!

18:51.350 --> 18:51.920
Ms. Xia!

18:52.750 --> 18:53.070
Cheers.

18:53.070 --> 18:53.880
-Ms. Xia.
-Ms. Xia.

18:53.880 --> 18:54.410
Alright.

18:54.790 --> 18:56.920
Thank you all for your hard work
during this time.

18:56.920 --> 18:57.920
I hope Qi Hang

18:58.160 --> 19:00.070
can be where your dreams set sail!

19:00.310 --> 19:01.070
Well said!

19:01.070 --> 19:01.920
Thank you, Ms. Xia!

19:01.920 --> 19:02.380
Cheers.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.540
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

19:05.680 --> 19:07.140
Hold her steady. Hold her.

19:07.240 --> 19:08.270
Mom.

19:08.830 --> 19:10.590
Promise we'll never be apart.

19:11.480 --> 19:12.610
Never apart. Never.

19:12.720 --> 19:13.310
We're leaving.

19:13.310 --> 19:14.550
Go ahead. Be careful.

19:14.550 --> 19:15.550
Watch the road. Be careful.

19:15.550 --> 19:16.510
Zhou Cheng, drive safely.

19:16.510 --> 19:17.440
Whose car is this?

19:17.440 --> 19:18.200
It's yours. Your car.

19:18.200 --> 19:19.830
Is it hybrid?

19:20.000 --> 19:20.480
What hybrid?

19:20.480 --> 19:21.160
Yes, it is...

19:21.160 --> 19:22.240
Renewable energy!

19:22.240 --> 19:23.680
Yes, yes. It is.

19:24.240 --> 19:25.300
Easy now. Careful.

19:25.510 --> 19:26.710
She's really wasted.

19:28.030 --> 19:29.310
Take her to Granny Yu's.

19:29.310 --> 19:30.690
I'll give Granny Yu a call.

19:30.690 --> 19:31.720
Don't worry, Uncle, Mrs. Liu.

19:31.720 --> 19:32.150
We're off.

19:32.150 --> 19:33.310
Sir, can we go now?

19:33.310 --> 19:33.640
Yeah.

19:33.640 --> 19:34.790
We can go. We're going.

19:34.790 --> 19:35.750
Watch your hand.

19:36.160 --> 19:36.750
We're off, Uncle.

19:36.750 --> 19:37.400
Be careful.

19:37.400 --> 19:38.200
Drive safely.

19:38.350 --> 19:38.720
Okay.

19:40.270 --> 19:41.270
Take care.

20:03.000 --> 20:03.720
Go inside.

20:14.350 --> 20:16.110
You're making me stay in this dump?

20:16.110 --> 20:18.440
You're lucky to have a roof
over your head.

20:18.590 --> 20:20.590
At least you're out of the elements.

20:22.000 --> 20:23.310
When will she see me?

20:23.720 --> 20:25.400
You didn't even handle things properly,

20:25.400 --> 20:27.130
yet you act all high and mighty?

20:27.590 --> 20:29.050
If you want to see Ms. Vivi,

20:29.830 --> 20:30.960
you'll have to wait.

20:47.110 --> 20:47.960
Officer Liu called me

20:47.960 --> 20:48.760
this morning.

20:49.240 --> 20:50.640
Zhang Tao and Zhang Bing have been caught,

20:50.640 --> 20:52.480
but neither of them has seen Ke Yixiong.

20:52.480 --> 20:54.480
They said they were acting on orders

20:54.750 --> 20:56.160
from someone called "Mosquito."

20:56.160 --> 20:57.290
Another scapegoat.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.200
Ke Yixiong got away again.

20:59.200 --> 20:59.750
That Ke Yixiong

20:59.750 --> 21:01.350
is really running out of men.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.110
This "Mosquito" guy
hadn't been with him for long.

21:03.110 --> 21:05.110
He was supposed to disappear
once the job was done,

21:05.110 --> 21:06.690
but he spent the money on whoring.

21:06.690 --> 21:08.000
After the police caught him,

21:08.000 --> 21:09.930
he gave up Ke Yixiong immediately.

21:10.200 --> 21:10.830
It's a pity

21:11.510 --> 21:13.070
that Ke still managed to escape.

21:13.070 --> 21:14.070
What a sly old fox.

21:15.590 --> 21:16.230
Ke Yixiong

21:16.230 --> 21:17.720
has a lot of cases hanging over him—

21:17.720 --> 21:18.960
robbery, theft,

21:19.220 --> 21:20.420
smuggling, and such.

21:20.880 --> 21:21.350
Longcheng has already

21:21.350 --> 21:23.150
issued a warrant for his arrest.

21:23.790 --> 21:25.160
As someone connected to him,

21:25.160 --> 21:25.750
you might also need to

21:25.750 --> 21:27.410
cooperate with questioning.

21:28.640 --> 21:29.370
You're here.

21:29.920 --> 21:30.520
Come on in.

21:31.070 --> 21:31.510
Okay.

21:35.040 --> 21:37.540
[Golden Sands Pool]

22:04.830 --> 22:05.830
This way, please.

22:06.510 --> 22:07.570
Thanks for coming.

22:10.480 --> 22:11.830
Please take a look at this apartment.

22:11.830 --> 22:12.680
This is our model unit.

22:12.680 --> 22:13.880
All of our model units

22:13.880 --> 22:15.880
are handled by Yuanhui Decoration.

22:15.890 --> 22:16.950
You can take a look.

22:22.680 --> 22:23.960
This here is one of the bedrooms,

22:23.960 --> 22:25.830
and it's also decorated by Yuanhui.

22:25.830 --> 22:27.070
Check it out. It's very spacious

22:27.070 --> 22:28.110
and comfortable.

22:29.310 --> 22:30.310
Hello, Ma'am.

22:31.790 --> 22:33.240
Why are these all marked?

22:33.270 --> 22:35.070
Yes, they're all sold out.

22:35.400 --> 22:35.830
Ma'am,

22:35.830 --> 22:36.960
why don't you come back tomorrow

22:36.960 --> 22:37.890
and check again?

22:38.070 --> 22:38.680
Because tomorrow

22:38.680 --> 22:40.160
is the payment deadline,

22:40.490 --> 22:41.590
and it's possible that

22:41.590 --> 22:43.160
some people still won't have gathered

22:43.160 --> 22:44.590
enough money by then.

22:44.950 --> 22:46.100
You might get lucky.

22:46.880 --> 22:48.480
There's one left over there!

22:51.510 --> 22:52.270
Ma'am,

22:52.440 --> 22:53.970
please come back tomorrow.

22:56.240 --> 22:57.640
Ma'am, I'll walk you out.

23:06.160 --> 23:06.690
Xiaolan.

23:12.440 --> 23:12.960
What?

23:13.350 --> 23:14.160
Did you see that Luo Yaozong

23:14.160 --> 23:15.160
has mostly recovered,

23:15.160 --> 23:16.880
so you came to ask for medical fees?

23:16.880 --> 23:17.830
You young lady,

23:18.520 --> 23:20.880
why do you always look down on people
like that?

23:20.880 --> 23:21.470
Our Luo family

23:21.470 --> 23:22.860
has never been that low.

23:23.830 --> 23:24.830
These past few days at the hospital,

23:24.830 --> 23:25.550
I've seen

23:25.880 --> 23:26.960
that you've been genuinely

23:26.960 --> 23:29.440
spending money and effort,
trying to save my grandson.

23:29.440 --> 23:30.790
I'm not the kind of person

23:30.790 --> 23:32.120
who likes owing favors.

23:32.640 --> 23:33.510
I came today

23:33.960 --> 23:35.480
because there's something

23:35.480 --> 23:36.940
I'd like to confess to you.

23:38.160 --> 23:38.830
So,

23:39.240 --> 23:40.440
you guys really were plotting against me

23:40.440 --> 23:41.300
behind my back.

23:42.880 --> 23:43.440
Forget it, forget it.

23:43.440 --> 23:44.700
I won't argue with you.

23:45.440 --> 23:47.830
Back then, when we went to cause trouble
at Golden Sands Pool—

23:47.830 --> 23:50.110
including having my grandson
work there as a security guard—

23:50.110 --> 23:52.030
someone paid us to do it.

23:53.240 --> 23:54.030
And

23:54.310 --> 23:56.310
that old matter from over 20 years ago—

23:56.310 --> 23:57.160
someone also had me

23:57.160 --> 23:58.960
deliberately tell you about it.

24:01.310 --> 24:02.310
Okay, I got it.

24:02.830 --> 24:03.920
Thank you, Chief Luo.

24:03.920 --> 24:04.920
You may leave now.

24:05.070 --> 24:05.680
So...

24:06.790 --> 24:08.110
So, are we even now?

24:10.270 --> 24:11.270
Even?

24:13.200 --> 24:13.790
Wait.

24:14.720 --> 24:16.160
You plotted against me,

24:16.160 --> 24:17.840
yet I spent money saving your grandson,

24:17.840 --> 24:19.900
and now you're telling me we're even?

24:22.750 --> 24:23.350
Forget it.

24:24.030 --> 24:25.750
If you say we're even, then we're even.

24:25.750 --> 24:26.350
Go on home.

24:27.920 --> 24:28.790
Thanks, then.

24:34.110 --> 24:35.510
Who do you think

24:35.510 --> 24:37.310
leaked Xu Zhongyi's info to you?

24:37.400 --> 24:39.460
At first, I suspected it was Xia Ziyu.

24:39.680 --> 24:40.310
After all, her reach

24:40.310 --> 24:41.880
extends all the way to Nie Weiguo.

24:41.880 --> 24:42.790
She even manipulated

24:42.790 --> 24:44.750
the design-drawing plagiarism incident.

24:44.750 --> 24:46.350
But later I thought about it—

24:46.720 --> 24:48.750
apart from you and my mom,

24:49.060 --> 24:50.920
no one else knows about Granny Yu.

24:51.070 --> 24:51.960
So there must be someone else

24:51.960 --> 24:52.760
in the middle—

24:53.270 --> 24:54.350
someone who's been sharing information

24:54.350 --> 24:55.160
with Xia Ziyu.

24:56.960 --> 24:57.620
Du Zhaohui?

24:59.310 --> 25:00.170
It can't be him.

25:02.350 --> 25:03.920
Anyway, we'll find out eventually.

25:03.920 --> 25:04.520
By the way,

25:04.920 --> 25:06.180
Jiang Yan told me today

25:06.270 --> 25:08.570
that Liu Tianquan had been arrested
in Shengcheng.

25:08.570 --> 25:10.170
He wouldn't be stupid enough

25:10.200 --> 25:12.630
to still dare come to Shengcheng
at a time like this, right?

25:12.630 --> 25:13.760
I guess Chairman Du

25:13.790 --> 25:15.320
sent him here to surrender.

25:15.830 --> 25:16.680
Anyway,

25:17.470 --> 25:18.380
Shi Kai's case

25:18.550 --> 25:20.410
has finally come to a conclusion.

25:25.070 --> 25:26.130
Prosecutor Liang.

25:28.750 --> 25:29.350
Wu Hao.

25:29.720 --> 25:30.920
Regarding this case,

25:30.960 --> 25:32.110
your Zhiyuan Law Firm

25:32.110 --> 25:33.240
really helped a lot.

25:33.510 --> 25:34.960
Whether for public duty
or personal reasons,

25:34.960 --> 25:36.090
we must do our utmost

25:36.220 --> 25:37.550
in Liu Tianquan's case.

25:37.750 --> 25:38.950
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

25:43.940 --> 25:48.260
[Shengcheng People's Court]

25:44.510 --> 25:45.510
Your Honor,

25:45.590 --> 25:46.790
members of the panel,

25:46.960 --> 25:48.560
today, as the public prosecutor,

25:48.560 --> 25:50.240
I bring charges against the defendant
in this case,

25:50.240 --> 25:51.040
Liu Tianquan.

25:52.000 --> 25:52.720
Shi Kai.

25:53.310 --> 25:55.110
We've finally reached this day.

25:56.030 --> 25:57.830
Liu Tianquan has been arrested,

25:58.110 --> 25:59.270
and Xiao Jianyong has testified

25:59.270 --> 26:00.730
to Liu Tianquan's crimes.

26:02.920 --> 26:04.580
For the truth and for justice,

26:04.950 --> 26:06.210
you gave your passion,

26:07.070 --> 26:08.130
and even your life.

26:10.270 --> 26:11.330
Justice prevails.

26:11.960 --> 26:13.620
Those who have scorned the law

26:14.400 --> 26:16.830
are about to face its judgment.

26:19.580 --> 26:25.540
[Sell One, Donate One Yuan]

26:22.070 --> 26:23.640
Please welcome Mr. Wu Qiang

26:23.640 --> 26:25.840
to present the award for Luna Clothing!

26:28.200 --> 26:29.110
Congrats. Congrats.

26:29.110 --> 26:30.310
Thank you. Thank you.

26:30.350 --> 26:30.720
Here.

26:30.750 --> 26:31.160
Okay.

26:31.240 --> 26:32.000
Keep up the good work.

26:32.000 --> 26:32.720
I will.

26:36.260 --> 26:37.500
Time flies.

26:38.350 --> 26:39.720
Everyone in Shengcheng

26:40.110 --> 26:41.440
is growing rapidly

26:41.790 --> 26:43.110
along with this city.

27:03.720 --> 27:05.450
Everyone is striding forward.

27:06.150 --> 27:07.950
But I, who never stopped moving,

27:08.920 --> 27:10.320
seem to have slowed down.

27:10.340 --> 27:13.540
[Qi Hang Property Co., Ltd]

27:12.680 --> 27:13.200
Ms. Xia,

27:13.680 --> 27:14.960
we are all curious about

27:14.960 --> 27:16.360
what your next plans are.

27:16.920 --> 27:18.530
I heard several Kong Island investors

27:18.530 --> 27:19.920
are coming to Shengcheng
to build properties.

27:19.920 --> 27:20.350
Yes.

27:21.030 --> 27:22.590
Kong Island investors
are both wealthy and capable,

27:22.590 --> 27:24.110
so they'll definitely go for
large-scale developments.

27:24.110 --> 27:24.750
There's no need for us

27:24.750 --> 27:26.410
to go head-to-head with them.

27:27.000 --> 27:28.400
For now, just finish

27:28.400 --> 27:29.600
the work at hand well.

27:29.880 --> 27:30.960
When a big project

27:30.960 --> 27:32.220
is finally confirmed,

27:32.350 --> 27:33.720
I hope each of you

27:33.750 --> 27:35.240
will be more mature than you are now

27:35.240 --> 27:37.500
and more capable of standing on your own.

27:37.640 --> 27:39.030
Rest assured, everyone.

27:39.030 --> 27:40.480
Since Qi Hang has set sail,

27:40.480 --> 27:41.480
it won't stop.

27:55.200 --> 27:56.930
It's starting. It's starting.

27:57.270 --> 27:57.800
Xiaolan.

27:58.000 --> 27:58.480
Xia Xiaolan.

27:58.480 --> 28:00.510
That custom drama you guys made—

28:00.590 --> 28:02.270
my grandma loves it so much.

28:02.270 --> 28:03.270
Every time, she asks me

28:03.270 --> 28:04.790
whether that character Cui

28:04.790 --> 28:06.210
was written based on me.

28:06.240 --> 28:07.960
She's been going around
telling all the neighbors about it.

28:07.960 --> 28:09.360
How's my scriptwriting?

28:09.480 --> 28:09.790
It's great.

28:09.790 --> 28:10.720
The characters in it

28:10.720 --> 28:12.180
do have traces of you guys,

28:12.460 --> 28:13.830
but for television purposes,

28:13.830 --> 28:15.880
they've been exaggerated and reshaped.

28:15.880 --> 28:16.750
The ratings for this show

28:16.750 --> 28:17.680
are pretty good,

28:17.830 --> 28:19.200
and sales in the store have also gone up.

28:19.200 --> 28:19.750
Yeah.

28:19.750 --> 28:20.270
That's right.

28:20.270 --> 28:21.800
Leading the fashion trend.

28:22.300 --> 28:24.950
I really envy you, Chen.

28:25.510 --> 28:27.110
When are you going to be a dad?

28:28.160 --> 28:29.090
Soon. Very soon.

28:32.400 --> 28:33.400
We are your fans.

28:33.400 --> 28:34.160
Can we get an autograph?

28:34.160 --> 28:34.830
One by one.

28:35.310 --> 28:36.960
Thank you. Thank you.

28:40.030 --> 28:41.560
Do you know how hard this is?

28:41.830 --> 28:42.350
Come on.

28:44.790 --> 28:45.450
Be careful.

28:46.510 --> 28:47.000
Here.

28:48.510 --> 28:49.410
Good job.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.680
Safety first. Keep it steady.

28:50.680 --> 28:52.070
Be careful not to spill the soup.

28:52.070 --> 28:52.510
Okay.

28:52.830 --> 28:54.110
Be careful. Ride slowly.

28:54.110 --> 28:55.570
Ride slowly. Ride slowly.

29:00.310 --> 29:01.970
Your business is really booming now.

29:01.970 --> 29:02.920
It's only been a short while,

29:02.920 --> 29:03.920
and there've been several delivery runs.

29:03.920 --> 29:04.790
Xiaolan is like

29:05.220 --> 29:07.410
the God of Wealth sent from heaven.

29:07.440 --> 29:08.270
There's no idea of hers

29:08.270 --> 29:09.830
that doesn't make money.

29:10.680 --> 29:11.200
Xia.

29:11.400 --> 29:12.240
I'm also curious about

29:12.240 --> 29:13.750
what your next plans are.

29:13.750 --> 29:15.400
Is there anything I can join in on?

29:15.400 --> 29:16.230
Some say

29:16.230 --> 29:18.000
you're going to Qiong Island
to speculate on land,

29:18.000 --> 29:19.030
some say

29:19.030 --> 29:20.400
you're going to Kong Island
to trade stocks,

29:20.400 --> 29:21.070
and others say

29:21.070 --> 29:22.440
you'll stay in Shengcheng

29:22.440 --> 29:23.750
to do commercial real estate.

29:23.750 --> 29:24.720
Which one is true?

29:24.720 --> 29:26.440
Well, can't I take a break?

29:26.440 --> 29:27.590
Do I have to keep spinning

29:27.590 --> 29:28.590
like a top?

29:28.880 --> 29:29.880
Besides,

29:30.030 --> 29:31.000
who said Qi Hang

29:31.000 --> 29:32.730
doesn't have any new projects?

29:32.960 --> 29:33.760
What project?

29:34.590 --> 29:36.110
It's still in preparation.

29:36.110 --> 29:37.000
No comment.

29:37.510 --> 29:39.240
Alright, alright. I won't ask.

29:41.240 --> 29:41.970
Look at this.

29:42.720 --> 29:44.050
Everyone's coupled up.

29:45.350 --> 29:46.030
These two

29:46.880 --> 29:48.210
are about to have a baby—

29:48.270 --> 29:49.640
a happy family.

29:50.200 --> 29:51.270
These two

29:51.720 --> 29:53.400
are just a marriage certificate away.

29:53.400 --> 29:54.240
And these two

29:54.400 --> 29:56.880
are passionately in love.

29:57.480 --> 29:58.680
I'm the only one left.

29:59.400 --> 30:00.510
So unlucky in love.

30:01.880 --> 30:02.640
Wei.

30:02.960 --> 30:04.510
You are so bitter.

30:04.640 --> 30:06.170
It's quite gross, you know?

30:07.000 --> 30:07.830
Since you like her,

30:07.830 --> 30:09.240
why don't you just tell her?

30:09.240 --> 30:10.790
You shower her with attention every day,

30:10.790 --> 30:12.050
but you won't confess.

30:12.200 --> 30:13.000
Don't tell me you just want

30:13.000 --> 30:14.130
to string her along.

30:14.440 --> 30:15.170
Xiaolan said

30:15.310 --> 30:17.270
people like that are called "scumbags."

30:17.270 --> 30:17.800
Scumbag.

30:18.000 --> 30:18.530
Scumbag.

30:18.640 --> 30:19.240
Scumbag.

30:20.070 --> 30:21.720
Don't talk nonsense.

30:21.750 --> 30:23.110
I've wanted to confess for a long time.

30:23.110 --> 30:24.640
I... I've even

30:24.640 --> 30:26.070
rehearsed my lines so many times.

30:26.070 --> 30:27.930
Ask Cheng if you don't believe me.

30:29.200 --> 30:29.600
Right.

30:29.880 --> 30:31.940
Every night in his dreams, he's like,

30:32.150 --> 30:32.880
"Li..."

30:34.440 --> 30:35.480
Alright, alright, that's enough.

30:35.480 --> 30:36.960
No need to go into details.

30:37.030 --> 30:37.640
No need?

30:37.640 --> 30:38.270
No need, no need.

30:38.270 --> 30:39.040
Wei.

30:39.070 --> 30:39.550
I know it's because

30:39.550 --> 30:41.020
you're worried since Li is already
under a lot of pressure,

30:41.020 --> 30:41.960
if you confess to her,

30:41.960 --> 30:43.640
it'll only make her feel
even more pressured, right?

30:43.640 --> 30:44.080
Look.

30:44.110 --> 30:45.400
Xiaolan understands me best.

30:45.400 --> 30:46.110
Soulmate.

30:46.680 --> 30:48.720
Li's mother's situation
is still uncertain.

30:48.720 --> 30:50.270
No one knows when she'll wake up.

30:50.270 --> 30:51.160
But Li can't possibly

30:51.160 --> 30:52.550
stay stuck where she is forever.

30:52.550 --> 30:53.160
One day she'll have to

30:53.160 --> 30:54.270
move forward.

30:54.790 --> 30:55.440
If you don't

30:55.440 --> 30:56.680
make things clear now

30:56.960 --> 30:58.030
and lose this chance,

30:58.030 --> 30:59.360
wouldn't that be a pity?

31:03.200 --> 31:04.270
Alright, don't be so depressed.

31:04.270 --> 31:05.270
Come on, let's have a drink.

31:05.270 --> 31:05.750
Cheers.

31:06.560 --> 31:07.930
Then let's wish that Wei

31:07.960 --> 31:08.960
won't be a scumbag.

31:08.960 --> 31:10.110
Hear, hear.

31:10.250 --> 31:10.790
To the scumbag.

31:10.790 --> 31:11.920
Don't be a scumbag!

31:13.910 --> 31:21.990
[Luna's Story]

31:23.880 --> 31:25.610
Got any new money-making plans

31:26.160 --> 31:28.020
that you can't even tell me about?

31:30.480 --> 31:32.270
I really haven't figured it out yet.

31:32.270 --> 31:33.310
That's why I didn't say anything.

31:33.310 --> 31:35.110
I'm not trying to be mysterious.

31:35.120 --> 31:35.930
However,

31:35.960 --> 31:37.790
I may not have a plan for making money,

31:37.790 --> 31:39.750
I do have one for spending it.

31:42.350 --> 31:43.310
What do you think about

31:43.310 --> 31:45.200
me setting up

31:45.480 --> 31:46.740
a student aid program?

31:48.110 --> 31:49.350
Would you also think

31:49.830 --> 31:51.520
that I've only just made a little money

31:51.520 --> 31:52.550
and I'm already getting ahead of myself,

31:52.550 --> 31:54.010
trying to play the savior?

31:55.790 --> 31:57.450
It's because of You Li, right?

31:57.640 --> 31:58.200
Besides,

31:58.830 --> 32:00.230
even if you were a savior,

32:00.550 --> 32:02.270
Darling, you'd definitely be

32:02.550 --> 32:04.680
a beautiful and kind-hearted savior.

32:09.350 --> 32:10.110
Zhou Cheng.

32:10.510 --> 32:11.400
You know what?

32:13.130 --> 32:14.410
In front of others,

32:14.510 --> 32:15.770
I don't dare to be smug.

32:16.030 --> 32:17.290
But only in front of you

32:17.480 --> 32:18.750
can I be like a child

32:18.750 --> 32:20.410
who got their favorite candy—

32:20.790 --> 32:21.880
carefree

32:22.070 --> 32:23.070
and carried away.

32:23.750 --> 32:24.950
That's because I know

32:25.200 --> 32:26.650
you're not just happy

32:26.680 --> 32:29.550
because you made money
from the Golden Sands Pool project.

32:29.550 --> 32:31.160
It's more about the whole process:

32:31.160 --> 32:31.960
the planning,

32:32.350 --> 32:32.960
the moves,

32:33.400 --> 32:34.400
and finally reaping the rewards—

32:34.400 --> 32:35.860
the joy of the entire game.

32:36.440 --> 32:37.000
You know,

32:37.680 --> 32:39.410
you earned the money honestly,

32:39.440 --> 32:41.310
so you should feel proud
and enjoy it to the fullest.

32:41.310 --> 32:44.160
Life's too short not to savor
your victories, you know.

32:44.160 --> 32:46.220
It was only then that I truly realized

32:47.120 --> 32:48.400
that the ability to flaunt

32:48.400 --> 32:50.000
or take pride in your success

32:50.310 --> 32:52.640
can be even more important
than success itself.

32:52.640 --> 32:53.840
But this idea of yours

32:54.310 --> 32:55.550
doesn't just require money—

32:55.550 --> 32:58.480
it also needs the cooperation of
the education authorities.

32:58.480 --> 32:59.920
Still, since you've decided to go for it,

32:59.920 --> 33:01.120
let's make it happen.

33:02.240 --> 33:03.310
Also,

33:03.400 --> 33:03.930
maybe...

33:04.420 --> 33:08.080
♪ Maybe all encounters in the world ♪

33:07.480 --> 33:08.200
Also,

33:08.290 --> 33:12.570
♪ Are predetermined by destiny ♪

33:09.510 --> 33:10.790
we should find a time

33:10.880 --> 33:12.880
to go get our marriage certificate.

33:14.330 --> 33:19.290
♪ The opening and closing chapters
are written ♪

33:17.240 --> 33:17.640
Okay.

33:20.020 --> 33:23.330
♪ From when we first met ♪

33:24.000 --> 33:27.830
♪ Till now, though much has changed ♪

33:30.100 --> 33:34.980
♪ Our hearts remain unchanged ♪

33:35.730 --> 33:40.670
♪ Having a dream in your eyes ♪

33:41.560 --> 33:50.840
♪ Time passes by,
yet I still love you the same ♪

33:51.490 --> 33:56.350
♪ After traveling through the crowds
and dark tides ♪

33:56.940 --> 34:06.100
♪ We must embrace
with the weight of the moment ♪

33:58.510 --> 33:59.240
Is it you?

34:00.110 --> 34:01.270
The voice that keeps

34:01.270 --> 34:02.480
hovering in my mind?

34:05.240 --> 34:07.500
Are you trying to remind me of something?

34:46.550 --> 34:47.679
You broke so easily.

34:53.800 --> 34:54.330
Mr. Kang.

34:58.190 --> 34:58.810
Mr. Kang.

35:02.030 --> 35:02.510
Li.

35:03.280 --> 35:03.740
Li.

35:03.880 --> 35:05.630
Kang, you're here again.

35:05.840 --> 35:06.510
This young man

35:06.510 --> 35:07.370
is really nice.

35:08.330 --> 35:08.970
Ms. Wang.

35:09.000 --> 35:10.110
He's my friend.

35:10.620 --> 35:12.030
I've been around long enough.

35:12.030 --> 35:13.490
Don't you think I can tell?

35:13.710 --> 35:14.360
It's just

35:14.590 --> 35:15.510
if you two

35:15.510 --> 35:16.770
don't make a move soon,

35:17.000 --> 35:18.480
the other young folks here

35:18.590 --> 35:20.050
won't be able to sit still.

35:23.960 --> 35:24.480
Li.

35:25.510 --> 35:26.910
Don't listen to Ms. Wang.

35:27.060 --> 35:28.950
Our conscience is clear.

35:29.070 --> 35:29.840
Friends are supposed to

35:29.840 --> 35:31.200
help each other out, right?

35:31.200 --> 35:32.200
Here, have a tangerine.

35:32.200 --> 35:33.400
You're always the one helping me.

35:33.400 --> 35:34.930
I haven't helped you at all.

35:35.960 --> 35:36.480
Fine.

35:36.480 --> 35:37.610
I'll be honest then.

35:37.960 --> 35:39.800
My conscience isn't exactly clear.

35:39.800 --> 35:40.760
So we're even.

35:43.400 --> 35:44.800
What are you laughing at?

35:45.200 --> 35:46.710
You're not making any sense.

35:46.710 --> 35:48.170
How does that make us even?

35:50.440 --> 35:51.110
Li.

35:51.960 --> 35:53.070
You know

35:53.230 --> 35:53.920
how I feel.

35:55.230 --> 35:56.110
Actually,

35:56.480 --> 35:57.280
it was only after

35:57.280 --> 35:59.230
learning about your family situation

35:59.230 --> 36:01.400
that I truly got to know you

36:01.760 --> 36:02.890
and understand you.

36:03.710 --> 36:04.840
You're a good girl.

36:05.880 --> 36:07.550
I know all your energy right now

36:07.550 --> 36:09.360
is focused on your mom's illness.

36:09.360 --> 36:11.880
You don't have the energy
to think about the future,

36:11.880 --> 36:13.190
and you don't dare to.

36:16.590 --> 36:17.250
Kang Wei...

36:18.480 --> 36:19.320
It's okay.

36:19.480 --> 36:20.610
I just want to say...

36:21.230 --> 36:21.960
Look,

36:21.960 --> 36:23.000
now that your boss

36:23.000 --> 36:23.880
is also my boss,

36:24.110 --> 36:25.570
we're sort of colleagues.

36:25.710 --> 36:27.510
We see each other every day.

36:27.880 --> 36:29.230
We still have plenty of time ahead.

36:29.230 --> 36:29.880
Anyway,

36:30.230 --> 36:31.230
I'll wait for you.

36:35.590 --> 36:36.190
Kang Wei.

36:37.880 --> 36:39.280
You're really nice to me,

36:40.030 --> 36:41.760
and I understand what you mean.

36:42.400 --> 36:43.190
But...

36:47.550 --> 36:48.000
Mom.

36:49.510 --> 36:50.030
Mom?

36:51.280 --> 36:51.840
Mom!

36:52.920 --> 36:53.360
Mom!

36:53.840 --> 36:54.280
You...

36:54.920 --> 36:55.440
Li.

36:55.670 --> 36:56.510
Her finger moved.

36:56.510 --> 36:57.510
Her finger moved!

36:57.760 --> 36:58.960
Nurse! Doctor!

36:59.110 --> 37:00.320
Can you hear me?

37:00.800 --> 37:02.070
It's Li, Mom.

37:07.800 --> 37:10.110
The patient's condition
has improved significantly,

37:10.110 --> 37:11.850
and she's regaining consciousness.

37:11.850 --> 37:13.190
We'll keep observing her.

37:13.190 --> 37:15.110
There's a good chance she'll wake up.

37:15.110 --> 37:16.510
Call me if anything happens.

37:16.510 --> 37:17.170
Thank you, Doctor.

37:17.170 --> 37:17.630
Thank you, Doctor.

37:17.630 --> 37:18.170
Thank you.

37:18.170 --> 37:18.770
Thank you.

37:20.590 --> 37:21.150
Mom.

37:25.590 --> 37:26.320
Don't worry.

37:26.360 --> 37:27.420
She'll get better.

37:29.110 --> 37:30.310
Thank you, everyone.

37:32.360 --> 37:32.840
Mom.

37:57.960 --> 37:58.510
Li.

37:59.590 --> 38:00.990
Cheng hired a caregiver.

38:01.150 --> 38:02.030
She'll come over this afternoon.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.070
You can try her out then.

38:03.070 --> 38:04.030
If she's good, keep her.

38:04.030 --> 38:04.550
If not,

38:04.550 --> 38:05.480
we'll hire someone else.

38:05.480 --> 38:06.630
Anyway, Xiaolan said

38:06.630 --> 38:07.320
we must find a suitable one

38:07.320 --> 38:08.250
for your mother.

38:09.030 --> 38:09.840
Thank you all.

38:10.810 --> 38:11.810
Don't mention it.

38:12.230 --> 38:13.710
Your mom is getting better day by day.

38:13.710 --> 38:15.040
We're all happy for you.

38:15.590 --> 38:16.360
And I believe

38:16.930 --> 38:17.680
that your mom

38:17.710 --> 38:19.040
will definitely wake up

38:19.110 --> 38:20.770
and talk to you again someday.

38:23.000 --> 38:23.800
By the way, Li,

38:24.360 --> 38:25.490
if your mom wakes up,

38:25.760 --> 38:27.290
what do you plan to tell her?

38:30.110 --> 38:31.360
I want to tell her

38:31.440 --> 38:33.240
what happened during this time.

38:33.550 --> 38:34.550
I want to tell her

38:34.710 --> 38:36.070
I have a great job

38:36.510 --> 38:38.310
and an amazing, wonderful boss.

38:39.070 --> 38:40.730
I also met a lot of good people.

38:41.230 --> 38:43.280
Although these days have been tiring,

38:43.280 --> 38:45.590
I feel happy every day,

38:46.150 --> 38:46.760
and I feel that the future

38:46.760 --> 38:47.880
is full of hope.

38:49.760 --> 38:51.400
I hope Mom can be like me—

38:52.440 --> 38:53.400
let go of the past

38:54.070 --> 38:55.070
and look forward.

38:57.030 --> 38:57.840
Well said.

38:58.440 --> 39:00.100
Your mom will surely be happy.

39:02.710 --> 39:04.770
I also want to tell her one more thing.

39:07.590 --> 39:09.280
That I met a very good person.

39:11.310 --> 39:13.140
Sometimes he's a bit clumsy,

39:14.000 --> 39:16.400
but sometimes he's a bit too quick-witted.

39:16.670 --> 39:17.710
He talks a lot,

39:18.400 --> 39:19.800
but he always means well.

39:20.550 --> 39:21.680
He is enthusiastic,

39:21.920 --> 39:22.550
brave,

39:22.710 --> 39:23.440
and kind.

39:24.920 --> 39:25.850
It may sound like

39:25.960 --> 39:27.710
nothing special,

39:30.320 --> 39:31.480
but in my heart,

39:32.360 --> 39:33.960
he's different from others.

39:35.880 --> 39:37.030
He has been by my side

39:37.030 --> 39:38.230
for a long, long time.

39:40.670 --> 39:41.480
Actually,

39:42.630 --> 39:44.490
I've wanted to tell him for a while

39:45.630 --> 39:46.690
that I like him too.

39:52.110 --> 39:52.800
Li.

39:53.360 --> 39:55.090
So you're willing to be with me?

39:57.840 --> 39:58.320
Um...

39:58.710 --> 39:59.190
Auntie,

39:59.510 --> 40:00.280
don't worry.

40:00.510 --> 40:02.230
I'll always treat Li well.

40:03.590 --> 40:04.790
Please rest assured.

40:10.590 --> 40:11.110
Mom.

40:25.670 --> 40:26.320
Hello, Ms. Xia.

40:26.320 --> 40:26.630
Morning.

40:26.630 --> 40:26.960
Good morning, Ms. Xia.

40:26.960 --> 40:27.230
Morning.

40:27.230 --> 40:28.090
Hello, Ms. Xia.

40:48.870 --> 40:50.620
[The 6th International
Youth Architectural Design Festival]

40:51.110 --> 40:52.240
But I didn't sign up.

40:59.400 --> 41:01.230
Today is
the foundation acceptance inspection

41:01.230 --> 41:03.760
for Phase II of
the Electronics City project.

41:03.800 --> 41:05.360
Why isn't Mr. Du here yet?

41:05.840 --> 41:06.360
What?

41:06.960 --> 41:08.190
Just because his status changed,

41:08.190 --> 41:09.920
now he's ignoring the business

41:10.120 --> 41:11.920
and doesn't care about
the groundwork anymore?

41:11.920 --> 41:12.710
It's not like that.

41:12.710 --> 41:14.190
Mr. Mao, please don't be angry.

41:14.190 --> 41:14.720
You know?

41:15.030 --> 41:15.840
There really is a lot

41:15.840 --> 41:17.070
going on in Kong Island.

41:17.070 --> 41:17.590
Right?

41:18.360 --> 41:19.070
So Young Master sent me

41:19.070 --> 41:20.600
to come work in Shengcheng.

41:21.920 --> 41:22.360
Hello?

41:23.000 --> 41:23.840
Hello? Hua.

41:24.150 --> 41:25.440
Are you with Mr. Mao?

41:25.670 --> 41:26.230
Yes, I am.

41:27.110 --> 41:27.630
Mr. Mao.

41:28.510 --> 41:29.320
Who is it?

41:29.710 --> 41:30.440
It's Ms. Xia.

41:32.360 --> 41:32.800
Hello?

41:33.760 --> 41:34.510
Mr. Mao.

41:34.960 --> 41:36.320
I received

41:36.320 --> 41:38.000
an invitation letter from

41:38.000 --> 41:39.280
the World Architecture Construction Federation.

41:39.280 --> 41:41.110
It says my Xinghe Theater project

41:41.110 --> 41:42.370
has been shortlisted.

41:43.320 --> 41:43.650
Good.

41:43.800 --> 41:46.230
Though I had the right to
make recommendations,

41:46.230 --> 41:47.690
the shortlisted projects

41:47.760 --> 41:49.280
were decided by the judges

41:49.360 --> 41:51.000
collectively.

41:53.630 --> 41:55.710
Your work truly earned it on its own.

41:56.400 --> 41:57.000
I heard

41:57.320 --> 42:00.050
this year's ceremony will be held
on Kong Island.

42:00.230 --> 42:02.070
You're finally making a name for yourself

42:02.070 --> 42:03.840
on the international stage.

42:04.510 --> 42:05.040
Alright.

42:08.510 --> 42:09.770
Hello? Hello? Ms. Xia?

42:10.280 --> 42:11.810
Congratulations, Ms. Xia.

42:11.960 --> 42:12.510
Hua.

42:12.710 --> 42:14.080
I'm going to Kong Island in a few days.

42:14.080 --> 42:15.030
Please help me make the arrangements.

42:15.030 --> 42:16.280
Okay, no problem.

42:16.480 --> 42:18.110
I'll call Young Master later

42:18.110 --> 42:20.030
and tell him to pick you up
at the checkpoint.

42:20.030 --> 42:20.630
Thank you.

42:24.440 --> 42:26.100
Kong Island Peninsula Hotel.

42:45.590 --> 42:47.650
I haven't opened this for a long time.

42:48.400 --> 42:50.000
The strings of numbers here

42:50.550 --> 42:51.480
are all from the despair I felt

42:51.480 --> 42:53.110
when my memory was in chaos.

42:54.010 --> 42:54.960
Thank you, Zhou Cheng,

42:54.960 --> 42:56.150
for pulling me out

42:56.150 --> 42:56.950
of this chaos.

42:57.740 --> 43:00.100
I still find it hard to let go,

43:01.150 --> 43:02.110
but I'm no longer afraid.
